A) sounds like a lot of fun, and<br>
B) is a way to thank guilds for helping with the mage epic, which is typically not used for the guild in any way.<br>
<br>
I can see this being effective in a few different iterations - bringing along say 10 epic mages and 2 clerics with group complete heal.  Those mages should be able to nuke at the limit of gaining aggro with sick amounts of mana given from Trods/Cheal.  6 Mages and 6 MB Wizzies - Mages could send in pets on dragon 'x', once pets wear down from AE, MB crew finishes dragon 'x'.  I'm sure there are more ways to do this.<br>
<br>
